name: 2 in 1 Embroidered Linen Purse
description:
I love the fabric on this purse! It's 100% linen and embroidered with a beautiful flower design. The inside of the purse is super soft velour. The big white button on the outside is actually on top of a small pocket (the pocket is kind of hard to see in the pictures) and there is one on the inside as well. There is also plenty of space in this lovely satchel for all your purse necessities! If you are like me, you need a LOT of room for them!

I can really see this purse on the arm of a beautiful, sophisticated lady (one who knows how to have a lot of fun!) walking down the street to the beat of her very own drum. Walk on!


If you have any questions ask! I'd be more than happy to answer them!

name: Strawberry Jumper Size 4T
description:
Big buttons = so amazing. And you won't find them much bigger than this! So patriotic, too!

Perfect summertime Jumper or even colder weather with a shirt underneath!

I love making clothes for little girls who want to express themselves and moms who like when their tots stand out!!

If you have any questions at all please feel free to ask, I'll be more than happy to answer them.
